"{\"uid\": \"hawaiinewsnow.com-sponsored-hawaii-symphony-orchestra-purchase-your-tickets-hawaii-symphony-orchestra-olympic-summer-romance-concert\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sponsored -The following content is created on behalf of Hawai\\u02bbi Symphony Orchestra and does not reflect the opinions of Gray Media or its editorial staff.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 57, \"end\": 64, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"score\": 0.9999956768379205, \"rank\": 4.309486215471989e-06, \"text\": \"Hawai\\u02bbi\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\"}, {\"begin\": 121, \"end\": 125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Edward_Gray\", \"score\": 0.999995754239908, \"rank\": 3.933371813488642e-06, \"text\": \"Gray\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Edward_Gray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Edward_Gray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To learn more about Hawai\\u02bbi Symphony Orchestra, visitwww.myhso.org    The Hawai'i Symphony Orchestra welcomes the community to enchanted evenings under the stars at the Tom Moffatt Waikiki Shell for the Sheraton Starlight Festival.\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 176, \"end\": 183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"score\": 0.9999956768379205, \"rank\": 4.309486215471989e-06, \"text\": \"Hawai\\u02bbi\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\"}, {\"begin\": 359, \"end\": 367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheraton_Hotels_and_Resorts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.867687814021629e-14, \"text\": \"Sheraton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheraton_Hotels_and_Resorts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheraton_Hotels_and_Resorts\"}, {\"begin\": 368, \"end\": 377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Starlight\", \"score\": 0.9999886772950333, \"rank\": 1.1322724441146338e-05, \"text\": \"Starlight\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Starlight\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Starlight\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 11-concert summer series features classical works, film scores, rock and pop music, and student performances.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our powerful storytelling is done through dynamic programs ranging from classical to hip and edgy to beloved film scores, offering something mesmerizing for everyone,\\\" said Dane Lam, music director for Hawai\\u02bbi Symphony Orchestra.\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 682, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mor_lam\", \"score\": 0.986096117558718, \"rank\": 0.01409258574379917, \"text\": \"Lam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mor_lam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mor_lam\"}, {\"begin\": 706, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"score\": 0.9999956768379205, \"rank\": 4.309486215471989e-06, \"text\": \"Hawai\\u02bbi\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Through a singular shared live experience, we hope to create joy, connection, and an eternal love of music.\\\"\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Concert goers can celebrate the 2024 Summer Olympics at the Olympic Summer Romance performance on Thursday, August 8.\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 962, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Under the baton of Director of Artistic Engagement Michael-Thomas Foumai, this carefully curated program features a dynamic selection of music that captures the spirit of competition and sportsmanship.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Attendees will hear the full orchestra perform the exhilarating Olympic Fanfare and Theme by John Williams, the musical emblem of slow-motion running, Chariots of Fire by Vangelis, the patriotic depth of James Horner's Apollo 13, and more.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Horner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Horner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Horner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Horner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Attendees of the Sheraton Starlight Festival can also look forward to hits from Elvis Presley, Lady Gaga, the Beatles, 80\\u2032s icons Madonna, Phil Collins and Queen, Disney classics from Moana and The Lion King, and so much more through August 18.For the full Sheraton Starlight Festival schedule, visitwww.myhso.org.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1423, \"end\": 1431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheraton_Hotels_and_Resorts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.867687814021629e-14, \"text\": \"Sheraton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheraton_Hotels_and_Resorts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheraton_Hotels_and_Resorts\"}, {\"begin\": 1432, \"end\": 1441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Starlight\", \"score\": 0.9999886772950333, \"rank\": 1.1322724441146338e-05, \"text\": \"Starlight\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Starlight\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Starlight\"}, {\"begin\": 1486, \"end\": 1499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elvis_Presley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4879881287322122e-25, \"text\": \"Elvis Presley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elvis_Presley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elvis_Presley\"}, {\"begin\": 1501, \"end\": 1510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 1536, \"end\": 1543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madonna\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.136308262245378e-32, \"text\": \"Madonna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madonna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madonna\"}, {\"begin\": 1545, \"end\": 1557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Collins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5513620117619634e-30, \"text\": \"Phil Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Collins\"}, {\"begin\": 1569, \"end\": 1575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Walt_Disney_Company\", \"score\": 0.999967721297763, \"rank\": 2.1292207521953562e-05, \"text\": \"Disney\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Walt_Disney_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Walt_Disney_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 1590, \"end\": 1595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moana_Hotel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.808039594826551e-17, \"text\": \"Moana\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moana_Hotel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moana_Hotel\"}, {\"begin\": 1600, \"end\": 1613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Lion_King\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.127916506385389e-27, \"text\": \"The Lion King\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Lion_King\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Lion_King\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Individual tickets begin at $15, or purchase four tickets for the price of three with Hawai\\u02bbi Symphony Orchestra's \\\"Me + 3\\u2033 discount - perfect for the whole 'ohana.\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1885, \"entities\": []}]}"